title: Fatboy Slim & The Chemical Brothers ? Rave on the Rocks (iPhone/
description: This show is a sure sign that Fatboy and the Chemicals have made inroads into the American musical consciousness that would have been unfathomable just five years ago. For all the talk of 1997's failed "electronica revolution," these two titans of dance music are about to play to a crowd of 8,000 lily-white suburban kids, 8,000 miles from Brighton, in a five-bucks-a-beer venue usually reserved for the Allman Brothers and Phish. Things have changed, and tonight, the revolution will even be televised.
